<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I&apos;ve read the first three so far. I don&apos;t think you have to read them in order to know what is happening, there will be spoilers, but nothing that tha<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I've read the first three so far. I don't think you have to read them in order to know what is happening, there will be spoilers, but nothing that that would prohibit you from still enjoying the other books. Reading them in order seems like it would be much more enjoyable though since there is a chronology. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
